survey_response.review_text:
Thank you soo much for  taking  great care in fixing  my partial flexible dentures. You always  make sure  I'm  comfortable during  each visit  and explain  in a way that I can understand. I'm  grateful for the  way you  help me keep  my smile  healthy. 
Your  patience  and  kindness  truly  make a difference Dr. Radhika Goel.

Doctor provided perfect consultancy, addressing all my concerns with clarity and professionalism. The teeth cleaning service was incredibly gentle, making the entire process comfortable and stress-free.

Dr. Radhika provides exceptional dental care with a gentle touch and thorough expertise. Their professionalism instills confidence, and their friendly demeanor puts patients at ease. From routine cleanings to complex procedures, Dr. Radhika ensures every visit is comfortable and informative, making them a trusted choice for dental health.
Very friendly behaviour and clear explanation of the problem by the doctor and its treatment.Hopefully the problem gets solved.

I'd been suffering from frequent cheek bites (every time I'd eat). Dr. Radhika did the bite correction procedure on my teeth. I felt no discomfort during the 5-minute procedure and I haven't had any cheek bites since. What's more, she discovered that one of my teeth had a cavity, something another dentist, whom I'd visited a few weeks earlier, had missed! Dr. Radhika filled the cavity and though I was expecting pain, I felt none. Also the filling material she used matched my tooth so well that when I was asked to check in the mirror, I couldn't tell which tooth had been worked on! It looks and feels absolutely natural. I also liked how she patiently answered all my queries before and after and explained the issues, possible solutions, and future actions in layman's terms and with easy to understand analogies. I liked the Dentotsav clinic as well. Everything on the premises looks neat and clean. The location itself is easy to find, especially on Google Maps. Moreover, the clinic has a very capable and polite staff. I was nervous before I got there but was made to feel comfortable as soon as I reached (Also, realizing that the clinic is equipped with the latest technology tools calmed my nerves further). All in all, it was a very satisfactory and pleasant experience (never thought I'd be using the word 'pleasant' to describe a visit to the dentist! :P). So, based on my visit and treatment, I believe that anyone seeking dental assistance would be in good hands with Dr. Radhika at Dentotsav.
My experience was very good .Doctor is very friendly with patient and her entire treatment procedure is excellent

Dr. Radhika has been my dentist for about a decade now and I have not been to any other dentist since being treated by her!

Before Dr. Radhika I had been to 4 other dentists in my life. 

The dentist experience had always left me rather scarred and shaken. But not with Dr. Radhika! She is so good that she even fixed a severe problem tooth which had been painful for about 2 years and for which I had been to so many dentists already!

As a gynecologist myself I can say that she has a fantastic work ethic. As a nervous dental patient I like how she explains everything really calmly and talks me through the procedure with a smile.

In the past I have had 2 completely painless root canals done by her. This time I got treated a for gap between my tooth which was causing food to be constantly stuck there, which led to cavities and toothache at the spot. I also got my broken front tooth fixed.

I guess what I like most about her is that she is able to destress the whole dental experience for me, while being very, very good at what she does.

The clinic is cozy and nicely maintained, with hygiene, cleanliness of top notch. The way one is welcomed with a bottle of packaged drinking water, is amazingly comforting. It may hardly cost anything, but it gives you a warm welcome feeling. I would strongly recommend Dentotsav and Dr Radhika V Goel, for all teeth related problems.

Dear Ma'am,

Sorry as we are to learn that you feel this way, we do appreciate you taking the time to give us this feedback!

Perhaps this rather Rare opinion stems from some sort of a misunderstanding, something for which we are very apologetic!

After all, thousands of patient's, (over more than a decade), couldn't all have been wrong all the time!

Our patients are from the whole cross-section of our society, be they college students, or retired govt. servants, or housewives, or businesspeople, or service personnel. This is obviously something we are deeply proud of!!

We believe in not bargaining with our patient's health and so we do not bargain with the quality of our care.

We also realized early on that the size of one's wallet has nothing to do with how beautiful one's healthy smile is! 

That is why we offer many Zero Interest payment plans, often spanning over several months, to many who are desirous of availing such facilities.

We are greatful you considered us and appreciate your trust in the quality of our care! 🙏

We look forward to seeing your happy smile again!

Regards,
TeamDentotsav🙂
